        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Grain population is a disconnected material aggregate which has crystallites ias parts.  Grain population represents grains which not necesserly spatially connected (unlike polycrystal) but share some collective quality, such as preffered crystallographic orientation.</rdfs:comment>
